           ┌─ Help ─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
           │ Probe Chat Shell Keys                                  │
           │                                                        │
           │ Enter / Ctrl+J      submit / newline                   │
           │ Up / Down           draft history recall               │
           │ Mouse wheel / PgUp  scroll active panel                │
           │ PgDn                scroll back toward latest          │
           │ Ctrl+O              add attachment placeholder         │
           │ Ctrl+R / Ctrl+S     backend check / backend overlay    │
           └────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘




